> Rent a wireless router
> Book a Japan Rail Pass before arrival
> Buy a Pasmo card or a Suica card
> Download the Hyperdia app for taxi booking
> Take advantage of discount rates on domestic flights
> If there's a choice, fly into Haneda, not Narita
> Book N'EX or Keisei from Narita
> Download Google Translate app for narrwing the language barrier
